title.rendered: B2B Matchmaking Event at KOSICT Technology Festival 2024 – October 11,2024

content.rendered:
We are excited to announce that during the KosICT Technology Festival 2024, Prishtina REA, in partnership with STIKK – Kosovo ICT Association and the Enterprise Europe Network – Kosovo, is organizing the B2B matchmaking event on October 11, 2024, in Prishtina, Kosovo.
 
This event aims to bring together international and local ICT business promoters, alongside panel sessions focusing on the success factors and challenges in developing and managing various innovation facilities. We will share valuable lessons learned from the business, startups, and digital nomads’ community users, leveraging this innovation capacity to achieve the digital and green ambitions of the Western Balkans.
 
Event Details:
 

Date

October 11, 2024

Venue

Tech Park Prishtina, Bërnicë e Epërme, 10000 Prishtinë

Web

KosICT

 

Target Sectors:


ICT & Digital Sector, E-services, Manufacturing, Clean Energy, Healthcare, Creative Industries This specially designed B2B event allows registered participants to identify the products and services of their interest while sending requests to relevant companies to organize pre-scheduled meetings.

We invite you to join us and participate to this impactful event, where we can collectively foster collaboration and innovation within the industry.
